trans-unit.source: Contains a strongly typed collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 物件的強類型集合。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElementCollection> class is used to work with a collection of <xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElementCollection>類別用來搭配集合<xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement>物件。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElementCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 建立新的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElementCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to add.
trans-unit.target: 要加入的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 加入集合。

trans-unit.source: Removes all <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> objects from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合中移除所有 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The key of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to find in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在集合中尋找的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> with the specified key exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />，指出具有指定索引鍵的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 是否存在於集合中。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the collection contains a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> with the specified key; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果集合包含具有指定索引鍵的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: An array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to which to copy the contents of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要將集合內容複製到其中的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 型別的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中以零起始的索引，複製作業從此處開始。

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements from the collection to an array, starting at a specified index of the array.
trans-unit.target: 從陣列的指定索引處開始，將集合中的元素複製到陣列。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to find in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在集合中尋找的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the zero-based index of a specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回集合中指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 的以零起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />, or -1 if the element was not found in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 的以零起始的索引；如果在集合中找不到此項目，則為 -1。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定集合中的項目。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index into the collection.
trans-unit.target: 集合中之以零起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the element at a specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定位在集合中指定索引處的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> that exists at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 在指定索引處的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: The key of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to get or set in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在集合中取得或設定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 之索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> that has the specified key in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定在集合中具有指定索引鍵的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 具有指定金鑰的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> with the specified key was not found in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 在集合中找不到具有指定索引鍵的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要從集合中移除的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: Removes a specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合中移除指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。

trans-unit.source: Removes a specified element from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合中移除指定的項目。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要從集合中移除的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 之以零起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Removes the element at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合中移除指定索引處的項目。

trans-unit.source: The key of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> to be removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要從集合中移除的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> 之索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Removes the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" /> with the specified key from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從集合中移除具有指定索引鍵的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElement" />。
